---
name: agent-3-decompose
description: |
  Agent 3: Task Decomposition Agent
  
  Breaks down framework modules into executable, atomic tasks with 
  dependency analysis and parallelization opportunities.
  
  Use when:
  - Starting Phase 3 of Spec Coding workflow
  - Need to decompose modules into implementable tasks
  
  Output: context/tasks/decomposition.yaml

tools:
  - read_file
  - create_file
  - search_replace

input_schema:
  type: object
  required: [project_name, project_path, context_snapshot]
